comment.text: This key displays the text for a "Delete" button or action, specifically used when deleting an agent. It appears within a context menu or similar UI element when managing agents within the application. Translators should ensure this conveys a clear and actionable deletion process.

usage.context:
id: "option_delete",
 key: "delete",
 label: isRootThirdPartyFolder
 ? t("Common:Disconnect")
 : isAIAgent
 ? t("DeleteAgent")
 : item.isTemplate
 ? t("DeleteTemplate")
 : item.isRoom
 ? t("Common:DeleteRoom")
 : t("Common:Delete"),
